Introduction 
Apache Solr (http://lucene.apache.org/solr/ ) is a open source enterprise search platform from the Apache Lucene project. 
Environment and Material 
•	Getting started with Solr(PPT) 
•	Java 1.5 or greater
•	Firefox browser & Poster Extensions
•	A Solr release: http://apache.mirrors.pair.com/lucene/solr/3.6.1/apache-solr-3.6.1.zip
Author 
•	Sally Tong 
Duration 
•	1.5 hours (always) 
Target Group 
•	people who is interested in search platform. 
Main Steps 
•	Introduction 
•	Exercise 1: install apache solr
•	Exercise 2: Feed data 
•	Exercise 3: Querying data
•	Exercise 4: Querying data Facet
•	Summary
Reference 
•	http://lucene.apache.org/solr/
